quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,135,"Yahuud e Nasaara en mbi'i ngonee Yahuuda maa Nasaara ndeen peewon wi': -aan annabiijo- accu dey min ngonata ko he diine Ibrahiima peewɗo oo ,etee o jeyanooka e sirkuɓe ɓee."
  2,136,"Mbi'ee min ngoongɗinii Alla e ko jippinaa dow amen e ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaak e Yaakuub e Asbaat e ko Muusaa e Iisaa okkaa e ko annabaaɓe ɓee okkaa iwde to joomiraawo maɓɓe min ceerndataa hay gooto e maɓɓe ko kamɓe min njebbilanii."
  2,137,"So tawii ɓe ngoonɗinii wano (hono) ko ngoonɗin-ɗon koo ndeen tawa ɓe peewii so ɓe ɗuurniima ndeen ɓe ngoni ko he luutndaade maa Alla suran ma ɓe ko Kanko woni nanoowo ngannduɗo fof."
  2,138,"Diine Alla neesuyaŋkeejo alaa diine ba'ɗe no diine Alla ɗee, minen ko Kanko min ndewata."
  2,139,"Wiy mbela on njeddondirat he amen fii Alla te ko Kanko woni joome amen e joome mon, min keɓat golle amen keɓon golle mon minen ko Kanko min laaɓanta."
  2,140,"Mbela on njiɗ wi'de wonde Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaaka e Yaakuub e Asbaat ɓe ngonndoo ko yahudeeɓe maa nasaaraɓe, wi' mbela ko onon ɓuri anndude Alla, hol mbo ɓuri tooñde oon cuuɗoowo seedanfaagu iwde he Alla, Alla noon yeebotaako ko ɓe ngollata koo."
  2,141,"Ngool ko leñol jawtungol engol heɓa ko ngol, fagginoo onon ne oɗon keɓa ko paggi-ɗon on naamnetaake ko ɓe ngollatnoo."